y across widefield, confocal, and multiphoton microscopy techniques.","kind":"page","category":"imaging","tags":["imaging","optical-sectioning-thickness","resolution","na","microscopy","airy","mtf","psf"],"priority":50},{"title":"Optical Waveguide Modes","href":"/wave-optics/optical-waveguide","description":"Slab waveguide mode analysis: V-number, NA, and effective index.","kind":"page","category":"wave-optics","tags":["wave-optics","optical-waveguide","gaussian beam","abcd","cavity","mode matching","diffraction"],"priority":50},{"title":"Orthoscopic Observation","href":"/polarization/orthoconoscopic","description":"Model orthoscopic observation of birefringent samples with rotating stage. Calculate intensity vs rotation angle and interference colors.","kind":"page","category":"polarization","tags":["polarization","orthoconoscopic","stokes","jones","mueller","waveplate","polarizer"],"priority":50},{"title":"OTDR Analysis","href":"/fiber-optics/otdr-analysis","description":"Simulate OTDR traces, calculate spatial resolution, dynamic range, dead zones, and event analysis for fiber characterization.","kind":"page","category":"fiber-optics","tags":["fiber-optics","otdr-analysis","fiber","mfd","na","dispersion","splice","coupling"],"priority":50},{"title":"PALM/STORM Localization Calculator","href":"/imaging/palm-storm","description":"Estimate effective resolution for single-molecule localization microscopy (PALM/STORM) based on localization precision and labeling density.","kind":"page","category":"imaging","tags":["imaging","palm-storm","resolution","na","microscopy","airy","mtf","psf"],"priority":50},{"title":"Parametric Amplification","href":"/wave-optics/parametric-amplification","description":"Optical parametric amplification (OPA) gain and bandwidth in χ⁽²⁾ nonlinear crystals.","kind":"page","category":"wave-optics","tags":["wave-optics","parametric-amplification","gaussian beam","abcd","cavity","mode matching","diffraction"],"priority":50},{"title":"Partial Refle