 refractive index affect the optical phase of reflected and transmitted light.","kind":"page","category":"thin-film","tags":["thin-film","phase-shift-coating","coating","ar","dielectric stack","bragg","reflectance"],"priority":50},{"title":"Photoacoustic Imaging Calculator","href":"/imaging/photoacoustic","description":"Imaging depth, resolution, and signal estimation for photoacoustic microscopy/tomography.","kind":"page","category":"imaging","tags":["imaging","photoacoustic","resolution","na","microscopy","airy","mtf","psf"],"priority":50},{"title":"Photodiode Speed","href":"/detectors/photodiode-speed","description":"Open Photodiode Speed.","kind":"page","category":"detectors","tags":["detectors","photodiode-speed","sensor","noise","qe","responsivity","nep","detectivity"],"priority":50},{"title":"Photoelastic Constants","href":"/materials/photoelastic","description":"Stress-induced birefringence: Δn = C · σ, where C is the stress-optic coefficient","kind":"page","category":"materials","tags":["materials","photoelastic","sellmeier","dispersion","glass","index","material properties"],"priority":50},{"title":"Photon Counting","href":"/detectors/photon-counting","description":"Open Photon Counting.","kind":"page","category":"detectors","tags":["detectors","photon-counting","sensor","noise","qe","responsivity","nep","detectivity"],"priority":50},{"title":"Photon Transfer","href":"/detectors/photon-transfer","description":"Open Photon Transfer.","kind":"page","category":"detectors","tags":["detectors","photon-transfer","sensor","noise","qe","responsivity","nep","detectivity"],"priority":50},{"title":"Photonic Bandgap","href":"/wave-optics/photonic-bandgap","description":"1D photonic crystal band structure and reflectivity.","kind":"page","category":"wave-optics","tags":["wave-optics","photonic-bandgap","gaussian beam","abcd","cavity","mode matching","diffraction"],"priority":50},{"title":"Photonic Crystal","href":"/fiber-optics/photonic-crystal","description":"Open Pho